[
    {
        "text": "Tia! I have good news!",
        "start": 20.36,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "Really? ",
        "start": 24.12,
        "duration": 0.84
    },
    {
        "text": "What is it Tofu? ",
        "start": 25.12,
        "duration": 1.24
    },
    {
        "text": "Tell me quickly! ",
        "start": 26.76,
        "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
        "text": "I have the option to become a part of either of the teams.",
        "start": 28.76,
        "duration": 4.24
    },
    {
        "text": "Both teams want me for next week’s match!",
        "start": 33.72,
        "duration": 3.32
    },
    {
        "text": "That’s wonderful! ",
        "start": 38.48,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "So what have you decided?",
        "start": 40.76,
        "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
        "text": "I haven’t decided as yet Tia",
        "start": 44.4,
        "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
        "text": "I am thinking ",
        "start": 47.48,
        "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
        "text": "I should see ",
        "start": 48.92,
        "duration": 1.24
    },
    {
        "text": "which of the two teams does better in the next few games. ",
        "start": 50.36,
        "duration": 4.6
    },
    {
        "text": "Then I will join the winning team. ",
        "start": 56.04,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "That’s not the right approach Tofu. ",
        "start": 60.72,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "It shows you to be cunning and disloyal.",
        "start": 63.36,
        "duration": 3.56
    },
    {
        "text": "Why?",
        "start": 68.96,
        "duration": 0.92
    },
    {
        "text": "well",
        "start": 71.32,
        "duration": 0.76
    },
    {
        "text": "Let me tell you the story of the bat, the beast and the birds.",
        "start": 72.08,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Once upon a time",
        "start": 97.96,
        "duration": 1.48
    },
    {
        "text": "in a dark jungle",
        "start": 101.16,
        "duration": 1.52
    },
    {
        "text": "there broke a dangerous fight ",
        "start": 103.36,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "between the beasts ",
        "start": 107.52,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "and the birds.",
        "start": 111.44,
        "duration": 1.24
    },
    {
        "text": "We will not tolerate the beasts any more. ",
        "start": 117.08,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "They feed on us",
        "start": 120.36,
        "duration": 1.24
    },
    {
        "text": "make preys out of our children ",
        "start": 121.92,
        "duration": 1.96
    },
    {
        "text": "and behave as if they are the rulers of the jungle. ",
        "start": 124.24,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes, yes! We agree with you our leader.",
        "start": 128.4,
        "duration": 3.56
    },
    {
        "text": "But we need more support from other birds.",
        "start": 132.6,
        "duration": 3.2
    },
    {
        "text": "Currently we are losing. ",
        "start": 136.52,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "We must reach out to every bird in the jungle to join our army. ",
        "start": 139.44,
        "duration": 5.56
    },
    {
        "text": "We shall find strength in numbers.",
        "start": 146.28,
        "duration": 2.52
    },
    {
        "text": " What do you say, Minister?",
        "start": 149.6,
        "duration": 1.96
    },
    {
        "text": "Everybody has agreed. ",
        "start": 152.52,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "We just need to ask the bats now. ",
        "start": 154.6,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "I am sure the bats will help us win. ",
        "start": 157.68,
        "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
        "text": "Very well then, invite their leader to our court.",
        "start": 161.56,
        "duration": 3.72
    },
    {
        "text": "The bat leader was invited to the court of the leader of the birds. ",
        "start": 170.24,
        "duration": 4.6
    },
    {
        "text": "Bat, we are in a war against the beasts.",
        "start": 181.68,
        "duration": 4.2
    },
    {
        "text": " Why don’t you join us? ",
        "start": 186.24,
        "duration": 1.52
    },
    {
        "text": "The bat leader wasn’t sure that it wanted to join an army that was losing. ",
        "start": 189.2,
        "duration": 6.08
    },
    {
        "text": "I am honoured by your offer",
        "start": 195.96,
        "duration": 2.2
    },
    {
        "text": "but I am afraid",
        "start": 198.72,
        "duration": 1.4
    },
    {
        "text": "I cannot join you. ",
        "start": 200.52,
        "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
        "text": "I am after all ",
        "start": 202.28,
        "duration": 2.12
    },
    {
        "text": "\"a beast\"",
        "start": 204.4,
        "duration": 1.08
    },
    {
        "text": "A few days passed. ",
        "start": 213.36,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "The beasts started losing.",
        "start": 218.24,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "We need to grow our army otherwise the birds will defeat us!",
        "start": 227.32,
        "duration": 5.08
    },
    {
        "text": "They drink from our lakes, live in our trees",
        "start": 233.12,
        "duration": 3.48
    },
    {
        "text": "yet, they behave as though they have more rights on the jungle than us. ",
        "start": 236.8,
        "duration": 5.32
    },
    {
        "text": "Minister! ",
        "start": 243.12,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "Who can help us win?",
        "start": 245.16,
        "duration": 1.8
    },
    {
        "text": "My leader, the only ones who have not joined the fight as yet are the bats.",
        "start": 248.24,
        "duration": 6.12
    },
    {
        "text": " We could ask them to join us. ",
        "start": 254.64,
        "duration": 2.36
    },
    {
        "text": "very well",
        "start": 258.08,
        "duration": 0.96
    },
    {
        "text": "Invite the bat leader to our court.",
        "start": 259.44,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "And so the bat leader was invited to the beast’s court. ",
        "start": 264.68,
        "duration": 4.92
    },
    {
        "text": "Bat, the war between the bird and the beasts of the forest is at its peak now",
        "start": 274.92,
        "duration": 6.8
    },
    {
        "text": "Whoever wins this last battle shall win the war and rule over the jungle. ",
        "start": 282.36,
        "duration": 6.24
    },
    {
        "text": "Why don’t you join us and help us win. ",
        "start": 289.44,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "You too will rule the jungle along with us",
        "start": 292.52,
        "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
        "text": "But the bat was once again unsure",
        "start": 297.48,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": " that it wanted to join the losing side with the beasts",
        "start": 301.36,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "I am honoured by your offer",
        "start": 306.6,
        "duration": 2.28
    },
    {
        "text": "But I cannot join you, as I am a bird. ",
        "start": 309.32,
        "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
        "text": "Just before the final battle was to take place",
        "start": 319.16,
        "duration": 3.96
    },
    {
        "text": "both the bird ",
        "start": 325.32,
        "duration": 1.32
    },
    {
        "text": "and beast leaders met",
        "start": 328.6,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "They were both upset by the losses their armies were suffering ",
        "start": 335.84,
        "duration": 4.12
    },
    {
        "text": "and decided to make peace",
        "start": 340.44,
        "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
        "text": "with one and other",
        "start": 343.28,
        "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
        "text": "The war was called off",
        "start": 348.64,
        "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
        "text": "We will not fight any more.",
        "start": 355.12,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes, we will live in peace now",
        "start": 358.16,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
        "text": "The whole jungle celebrated the new peace in the land",
        "start": 363.48,
        "duration": 4.36
    },
    {
        "text": "When the Bat leader heard of this development",
        "start": 375.32,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "he went to the birds and asked to be a part of the celebration",
        "start": 380.84,
        "duration": 4.36
    },
    {
        "text": "But the Bird Leader remembered ",
        "start": 389.8,
        "duration": 2.12
    },
    {
        "text": "how the Bat leader had refused to help the birds",
        "start": 392.2,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "during the war ",
        "start": 395.88,
        "duration": 0.96
    },
    {
        "text": "and turned him and his kind away",
        "start": 397.12,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "No bird would even talk to them now",
        "start": 401.28,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
        "text": "The Bat Leader knew that if he took his people to the beasts",
        "start": 406.0,
        "duration": 4.6
    },
    {
        "text": "they would simply tear them apart. ",
        "start": 410.6,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "And so he did not approach them",
        "start": 414.4,
        "duration": 2.48
    },
    {
        "text": "Hence",
        "start": 419.28,
        "duration": 1.04
    },
    {
        "text": "he and his entire kind ",
        "start": 420.32,
        "duration": 2.2
    },
    {
        "text": "lived in isolation without any friends in the jungle",
        "start": 422.52,
        "duration": 4.92
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh! I don’t want to be alone, Tia! ",
        "start": 430.16,
        "duration": 3.76
    },
    {
        "text": "In that case Tofu",
        "start": 435.68,
        "duration": 1.72
    },
    {
        "text": "you should not behave cunningly like the Bat Leader ",
        "start": 437.4,
        "duration": 3.8
    },
    {
        "text": "and you should inform the team\nthat you want to join",
        "start": 441.88,
        "duration": 3.24
    },
    {
        "text": "right away. ",
        "start": 445.12,
        "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes, Tia. I will do that right away. ",
        "start": 447.72,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank you Tia",
        "start": 454.96,
        "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
        "text": "for making me understand this",
        "start": 456.48,
        "duration": 2.24
    }
]